   521	## §E CLI changes
   522	
   523	None. The web-ui's existing flags are sufficient. Specifically:
   524	
   525	- `--repo-path` was already optional; chunk 9e widens its consumer
   526	  set (work-ref GC reads it) without changing the flag's
