   623	
   624	### `test_admin_flow.py` — cross-request flow
   625	
   626	- Sign in → claim a task via planner → admin dashboard reflects
   627	  the claim → operator-reclaim from admin → planner page no
   628	  longer claims that task. End-to-end flows that span modules.
   629	- Sign in → submit a task via implementer → admin sees `submitted`
   630	  → operator force-reclaim → admin sees `pending`.
   631	- Sign in → planner submits a proposal → admin trial detail page
